snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - Official Skulls Showcase Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 is an upcoming third-person shooter that has shown off gameplay during the Skulls Showcase. Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 is launching on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series S|X, and PC at a later date.

#IGN #Warhammer #Gaming
